# Security Review Requirements
# Global code owners for security-critical files

# Infrastructure and Security Configuration
terraform/                    @security-team @platform-team
terragrunt/                   @security-team @platform-team
kubernetes/policies/          @security-team @k8s-team
.github/workflows/            @security-team @devops-team

# Application Security
app/                         @security-team @dev-team
Dockerfile                   @security-team @dev-team

# Compliance and Documentation
docs/                        @security-team @compliance-team
*.md                         @security-team

# Security-Critical Files (Require 2 approvals)
**/*security*                @security-team @security-lead
**/*compliance*              @security-team @compliance-team
**/policies/                 @security-team @security-lead

# Environment-Specific Overrides
terraform/environments/production/  @security-lead @platform-lead
terragrunt/environments/production/ @security-lead @platform-lead